G:jeo orchestration annotate ui-review agentui ralph plannotator omc omx ohmg bmad agent-browser agentation multi-agent workflow resume continue-from-.jeo cleanup browser-verification ui-feedback submit-gate onsubmit 오케스튤 계획 실행 검증 정리 재개

U[5]:
  Run the repo's end-to-end agent workflow: planning -> execution -> QA -> cleanup
  Keep a durable `.jeo` ledger with long-term rules, short-term plans, queued work, progress, and history
  Resume an existing workflow instead of rebuilding planning/task structure from scratch
