  Never enter EXECUTE without plan approval
  Never run plannotator or agentation in background mode with `&`
  JEO is the router, not the owner of ralph/plannotator/agent-browser/agentation/runtime internals
  Respect the explicit submit/onSubmit gate before processing annotations
  Persist state in `.omc/state/jeo-state.json` and durable workflow context in `.jeo/`
